  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Delhi</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Delhi has extreme seasons — from 45°C summer heat to near-freezing winter fog. October to March is the best time: cool, pleasant and the city's cultural life at its richest. Avoid May-June (extreme heat) and July-August (humidity). Delhi's winter fog (December-January) creates a haunting atmosphere around its monuments.</p>
